</div>
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" source="#iaph2007">
            <p>No translation possible</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>This could be an assembly number, but it is clearly cut and very visible; just possibly a label, e.g. <foreign xml:lang="grc">
                  <persName type="other">
                     <expan>
                        <abbr>Θ</abbr>
                        <ex>ησεύς</ex>
                     </expan>
                  </persName>
               </foreign> for the young hero below.</p>
            <p>For a description of the panel see P. Linant de Bellefonds, <title>Aph.Papers</title> III, 174-86, 175-7.</p>
         </div>
